    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Caecilio Metello <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulo</ex></expan> Licinio co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>ecimus</ex></expan> Iulius <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>ecimi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> Cilo hospitium fecit <lb n="3"/>sibi liberis posterisque suis cum Nigro <lb n="4"/>et Rufo et Prisco Turdulis Veteribus <lb n="5"/>liberis posterisque eorum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hospitium-Vertrag. Stamm der Turduli Veteres (s. Pomp. Mela, chorogr. 3, 8; Plin., nat. 4,112-113) hier und in AE 1983,477 erstmals inschriftlich belegt.</p>
            </div>
